  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"page77R_mcid13\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Keywords:</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">Genjutsu</span><span dir=\"ltr\">, Tactile</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"markedContent\">A beam of shifting Psychic energy of your design or description streaks towards a creature within range.<br /> Make a ranged genjutsu attack against the target.<br /> On hit, the target takes 1d10 Psychic damage.<br /> At Higher Levels: This genjutsu can create more than one beam when you reach higher levels.<br /> Up to two beams at 5th level, three beams at 11th level, four beams at 17th level.<br /> You can direct the beams at the same target or different ones.<br /> Make a separate attack roll for each beam.<br /></span></p>",
